select  count(distinct a.tracking_message_header) from
(
select tracking_message_header, 
from_unixtime(log_time) as log_time,
message from gmonstar_orchestration_1_8.audit_log
 where is_successful = 1
 and message  like "%/profileSwitch%" 
 and value like "%profileSwitchState:Begun%"
and tracking_message_header in 
(
select tracking_message_header 
 from gmonstar_orchestration_1_8.audit_log where parent_api_name = "UpdateSimProfile"
 and  $__unixEpochFilter(log_time)))a
 
inner join
(
select tracking_message_header from 
(
select tracking_message_header , substring_index(substring_index(value,'|#@|',1),'|#@|',1) as imsi
 from gmonstar_orchestration_1_8.audit_log where parent_api_name = "UpdateSimProfile"
 and   $__unixEpochFilter(log_time) )d
where d.imsi = "AE")b
ON a.tracking_message_header = b.tracking_message_header
